Discover our fresh approach to service and support

At primeForce, we prioritize the success of your business. That starts with customer-driven innovation and our powerful, intuitive platform. But beyond the technology, we develop long-term partnerships with our customers, working together to achieve your most important business goals.

Here’s what to expect as an primeForce customer:

  • Support from our award-winning customer service team

  • On-demand access to product knowledge resources, including self-guided and live online training

  • Events and webinars to keep your team up-to-date on new features and how to use them

We partner with you for a smooth transition

As your technology partner, we get right to work when you’ve chosen us to support your business. That means our team actively supports you throughout the entire onboarding process, so you and your teams won’t miss a beat. We’ll learn about your unique business goals first to accelerate the return on your technology investment.

  • Maintain productivity and keep your monthly accounting process on track while you make the switch with on-call implementation and onboarding specialists

  • Maximize your use of primeForce’s features with instant, on-demand access to primeForce’s product training and guided tutorials
